rjordan

Many thanks - and impressive collection of kit you have!

Angri1... your welcome, my pleasure.  It's been years of slow upgrades.

insinuendo.... if it was someone else's rip I would have given them the credit as that seems to be the respectful/honest thing to do.  It's mine.

Just checkin'. 

Asides the continuous, yet tolerable surface noise, I must say I am pleasantly surprised. 

Nice work!
